Cs_siena - hostage-rescue

Counter-Terrorists: Save the 4 hostages located at the library.

Terrorists: Prevent the counter-terrorists from rescuing the hostages.

Notes: Siena, like many other Tuscan hill towns, was first settled in the time of the Etruscans (circa 900BC to 400BC) when it was inhabited by a tribe called the Saina.
